How to Run

1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/kanishkdutta22/credit-card-fraud-detection
cd credit-card-fraud-detection


2. Install dependencies
pip install pandas numpy matplotlib seaborn scikit-learn imbalanced-learn


3. Download the dataset from Kaggle and place creditcard.csv in the project root

4. Run the pipeline
python credit_card_fraud_detection.py


The script runs end-to-end — EDA → preprocessing → SMOTE → training → evaluation → visualisations → model save. All plots are saved as .png files in the project root.
